{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813371946,"sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","part":{"id":"prt_d76b9a3d30010wIHOxZxzehY8J","messageID":"msg_d76b992c8001CQ05FwcsydR5xX","sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_8b5592ff5be346fb8c433552","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立 HTTP 服务框架，提供 WorkloadManager 的 RESTful API 接口层，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心控制面入口。\n6: \n7: ## 元信息\n8: \n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n10: - **Language**: Go\n11: - **Size**: M\n12: \n13: ## 目的\n14: \n15: WorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 的核心控制面组件，负责通过 Kubernetes API 管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的生命周期（创建、查询、更新、删除沙箱会话）。本变更将建立完整的 HTTP 服务框架，使 Router、CLI 和 SDK 等下游消费者能够通过标准化的 RESTful API 与 WorkloadManager 交互，实现沙箱的创建、查询、销毁和状态管理。\n16: \n17: 具体目标：\n18: 1. 提供统一的 HTTP 服务启动/停止生命周期管理\n19: 2. 暴露 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 CRUD 端点\n20: 3. 提供健康检查端点供 Kubernetes 探针使用\n21: 4. 建立请求日志、恢复和验证中间件基础设施\n22: 5. 为 AR-005+ 的会话管理、沙箱调度等高级功能提供可扩展的 HTTP 基座\n23: \n24: ## 范围\n25: \n26: ### 包含\n27: \n28: 1. **HTTP 框架选型与集成** — 引入 `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` 作为 HTTP 框架，与项目现有 Go 1.24.4 工具链和 k8s.io 依赖兼容\n29: 2. **服务结构体** — `Server` struct 封装 `*gin.Engine`、`*http.Server`、配置和 Kubernetes clientset\n30: 3. **路由注册** — 按 RESTful 约定注册以下端点：\n31:    | Method | Path | 说明 |\n32:    |--------|------|------|\n33:    | GET | `/health` | 健康检查（liveness + readiness 共用） |\n34:    | POST | `/v1/agent-runtime` | 创建 AgentRuntime 沙箱 |\n35:    | GET | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 查询 AgentRuntime |\n36:    | PUT | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 更新 AgentRuntime |\n37:    | DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n38:    | POST | `/v1/code-interpreter` | 创建 CodeInterpreter 沙箱 |\n39:    | GET | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 查询 CodeInterpreter |\n40:    | PUT | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 更新 CodeInterpreter |\n41:    | DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n42: 4. **Handler 层** — 每个端点对应的 handler 函数，通过 AR-003 定义的共享类型和 AR-001/AR-002 的 CRD 类型与 Kubernetes API 交互\n43: 5. **中间件** — `gin.Logger`（请求日志）、`gin.Recovery`（panic 恢复）、请求 ID 追踪\n44: 6. **配置结构体** — `Config` struct（Port、DebugMode、KubeConfig 路径等）\n45: 7. **优雅关闭** — 通过 `context.Context` 和 `http.Server.Shutdown()` 实现优雅停机\n46: 8. **错误响应统一格式** — 标准 JSON 错误体 `{\"error\": \"message\", \"code\": int}`\n47: 9. **单元测试** — Handler 层使用 fake clientset 进行隔离测试\n48: \n49: ### 不包含\n50: \n51: - Kubernetes Informer/Controller 模式的重调和逻辑（后续变更）\n52: - 沙箱会话的 Redis 状态管理（由 Router + Session Store 负责）\n53: - JWT 认证和鉴权（Router 层负责，WorkloadManager 通过 in-cluster ServiceAccount 信任）\n54: - CodeInterpreter 代码执行引擎（PicoD 职责）\n55: - Helm Chart 部署配置（已有 deployment spec 覆盖）\n56: - E2E 测试（独立变更项）\n57: \n58: ## 服务结构概要\n59: \n60: ```\n61: pkg/workloadmanager/\n62: ├── server.go              # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n63: ├── config.go              # Config struct, 默认值, 环境变量读取\n64: ├── routes.go              # 路由注册, SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine)\n65: ├── handler/\n66: │   ├── health.go          # GET /health handler\n67: │   ├── agent_runtime.go   # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n68: │   └── code_interpreter.go # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n69: ├── middleware/\n70: │   ├── logger.go          # 请求日志中间件（可选，复用 gin.Logger）\n71: │   └── recovery.go        # Panic 恢复中间件（可选，复用 gin.Recovery）\n72: ├── response/\n73: │   └── response.go        # 统一 JSON 响应格式 helper\n74: ├── server_test.go         # Server 生命周期测试\n75: ├── handler/\n76: │   ├── health_test.go     # 健康检查 handler 测试\n77: │   ├── agent_runtime_test.go  # AgentRuntime handler 测试\n78: │   └── code_interpreter_test.go # CodeInterpreter handler 测试\n79: └── response/\n80:     └── response_test.go   # 响应格式 helper 测试\n81: ```\n82: \n83: ### Server struct\n84: \n85: ```go\n86: type Server struct {\n87:     config    *Config\n88:     engine    *gin.Engine\n89:     httpSrv   *http.Server\n90:     clientset clientset.Interface  // AR-004 生成的 client-go\n91: }\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ### Config struct\n95: \n96: ```go\n97: type Config struct {\n98:     Port         int    // 默认 8080\n99:     KubeConfig   string // 默认空（in-cluster config）\n100:     Debug        bool   // 默认 false\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: ### 健康响应格式\n105: \n106: - 正常: `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n107: - 异常: `{\"status\": \"error\", \"error\": \"reason\"}`\n108: \n109: ## 影响分析\n110: \n111: ### 直接影响\n112: \n113: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n114: |------|------|------|\n115: | `pkg/workloadmanager/` | 新增 | 完整的 HTTP 服务框架目录和文件 |\n116: | `go.mod` | 新增依赖 | 需添加 `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` |\n117: | `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` | 新增或修改 | 服务启动入口，调用 `pkg/workloadmanager.NewServer()` 和 `Run()` |\n118: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/` | 新增 | CRUD handler 实现，依赖 `client-go` 生成的 typed client |\n119: | `pkg/workloadmanager/response/` | 新增 | 统一响应格式 helper |\n120: \n121: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n122: \n123: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n124: |------|----------|\n125: | Router（session-routing） | 通过 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 调用本变更暴露的 `/v1/agent-runtime` 和 `/v1/code-interpreter` 端点 |\n126: | CLI 工具 | 通过 HTTP API 直接管理沙箱生命周期 |\n127: | Python SDK | 封装本变更的 HTTP 端点为用户提供 Python 接口 |\n128: | E2E 测试 | 验证沙箱创建、查询、删除的完整流程 |\n129: \n130: ### 无影响的组件\n131: \n132: - `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` — API 类型定义已完成（AR-001/AR-002/AR-003），本变更仅消费\n133: - `client-go/` — 已生成的 typed client 代码不受影响，本变更是其消费者\n134: - Session Store（Redis/Valkey）— 存储层独立，WorkloadManager 不直接操作 Redis\n135: - Agentd（idle cleanup）— 通过 store 接口交互，不依赖 WorkloadManager HTTP API\n136: - PicoD（code execution）— 沙箱内组件，与控制面 HTTP 框架无关\n137: - Helm Chart — 部署配置已存在，本变更不改变服务暴露方式（仍为 port 8080 + `/health`）\n138: \n139: ## 备选方案\n140: \n141: ### 方案 A：Gin 框架（已选）\n142: \n143: **优点**：Router 组件（session-routing）已选用 Gin 作为 HTTP 框架，保持技术栈统一；Gin 生态成熟、社区活跃、中间件丰富；性能优秀（基于 httprouter）；与 Go 1.24.4 兼容良好；学习成本低，团队熟悉度高。\n144: **缺点**：引入额外的第三方依赖；Gin v1 已停止大版本更新（但维护稳定）。\n145: \n146: ### 方案 B：标准库 `net/http` + `http.ServeMux`\n147: \n148: **优点**：零额外依赖；Go 1.22+ 的 `ServeMux` 支持方法匹配和路径参数，功能已较完善；长期维护有保障。\n149: **缺点**：缺少内置的中间件链、请求绑定、JSON 验证等便利功能；需要自行实现 panic recovery 和结构化日志；与 Router 组件的技术栈不一致，增加维护认知负担。**否决**。\n150: \n151: ### 方案 C：Echo 框架\n152: \n153: **优点**：API 设计优雅；内置数据绑定和验证；中间件生态丰富。\n154: **缺点**：与 Router 组件的 Gin 技术栈不一致；引入第二个 HTTP 框架增加依赖管理复杂度；团队对 Gin 更熟悉。**否决**。\n155: \n156: ### 方案 D：chi 路由器\n157: \n158: **优点**：轻量级、符合 stdlib 风格；中间件通过独立包提供；与 `net/http` 完全兼容。\n159: **缺点**：缺少内置的 JSON 绑定和验证；需要组合多个包才能达到 Gin 的开箱即用体验；与 Router 组件技术栈不一致。**否决**。\n160: \n161: ### 方案 E：controller-runtime 的 `webhook.Server` / `manager` 模式\n162: \n163: **优点**：与 Kubernetes 控制器生态深度集成；内置 leader election、health probes、metrics。\n164: **缺点**：本变更仅需 HTTP API 服务，不需要完整的控制器运行时；controller-runtime 的 manager 模式过于重量级（M 规模的变更引入过大依赖面）；Router 组件不使用此模式，技术栈分裂。**否决**（可在后续需要 Reconciler 时另行引入）。\n165: \n166: ## 验收标准\n167: \n168: 1. `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n169: 2. `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n170: 3. `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` 已添加到 `go.mod` 且 `go mod tidy` 无冲突\n171: 4. 服务启动后监听配置的端口（默认 8080）\n172: 5. `GET /health` 返回 `200 OK` 且响应体为 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n173: 6. `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 接收合法 AgentRuntime 定义，通过 fake clientset 返回 `200 OK` 及资源信息\n174: 7. `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 接收缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，返回 `400 Bad Request`\n175: 8. `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 接收合法 CodeInterpreter 定义，通过 fake clientset 返回 `200 OK`\n176: 9. 相同 `name` 的连续创建请求行为符合 Kubernetes CRD 语义（Update 或 Conflict）\n177: 10. 服务支持优雅关闭：收到 SIGTERM/SIGINT 后完成现有请求再退出\n178: 11. Gin 模式在 `Config.Debug=false` 时为 `ReleaseMode`，`true` 时为 `DebugMode`\n179: 12. 所有 handler 使用统一的 JSON 错误响应格式 `{\"error\": \"message\"}`\n180: \n181: ## 状态\n182: \n183: - [ ] 提案审查\n184: - [ ] 实现\n185: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 185 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## 概述\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立 HTTP 服务框架，提供 WorkloadManager 的 RESTful API 接口层，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心控制面入口。\n\n## 元信息\n\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n\n## 目的\n\nWorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 的核心控制面组件，负责通过 Kubernetes API 管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的生命周期（创建、查询、更新、删除沙箱会话）。本变更将建立完整的 HTTP 服务框架，使 Router、CLI 和 SDK 等下游消费者能够通过标准化的 RESTful API 与 WorkloadManager 交互，实现沙箱的创建、查询、销毁和状态管理。\n\n具体目标：\n1. 提供统一的 HTTP 服务启动/停止生命周期管理\n2. 暴露 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 CRUD 端点\n3. 提供健康检查端点供 Kubernetes 探针使用","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775813371934,"end":1775813371944}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813373316,"sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","part":{"id":"prt_d76b9a89a001A0gzp84MeRwTUh","messageID":"msg_d76b992c8001CQ05FwcsydR5xX","sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_23fe0d38b88948169394579c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: <!-- TODO: 填写架构定位 -->\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 包结构\n10: \n11: <!-- TODO: 填写包结构 -->\n12: \n13: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n14: \n15: <!-- TODO: 填写依赖关系 -->\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## 2. 数据结构\n20: \n21: <!-- TODO: 填写数据结构 -->\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## 3. 测试策略\n26: \n27: <!-- TODO: 填写测试策略 -->\n28: \n29: ---\n30: \n31: ## 4. 实现步骤\n32: \n33: ### 4.1 文件创建的顺序\n34: \n35: <!-- TODO: 填写实现步骤 -->\n36: \n37: ### 4.2 验证检查清单\n38: \n39: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n40: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 全部通过\n\n(End of file - total 40 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写架构定位 -->\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写包结构 -->\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写依赖关系 -->\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775813373308,"end":1775813373314}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813374406,"sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","part":{"id":"prt_d76b9adea001y7MqC3OqaWyiTb","messageID":"msg_d76b992c8001CQ05FwcsydR5xX","sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_e0b3999aecfa466d93c08097","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # delta-spec: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n6: **Language:** Go  \n7: **Size:** M  \n8: \n9: WorkloadManager 提供 HTTP 服务框架，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载的生命周期。基于 `client-go` 生成的 Kubernetes typed client 与 informer 机制，对外暴露 RESTful API。\n10: \n11: ---\n12: \n13: ## Requirement: HTTP Server 初始化与生命周期\n14: \n15: **ID:** REQ-001  \n16: **Priority:** P0  \n17: \n18: 系统 MUST 提供一个可配置的 HTTP 服务器，支持 graceful shutdown。\n19: \n20: ### Scenario: 服务器正常启动\n21: \n22: **GIVEN** 有效的监听地址和端口配置  \n23: **WHEN** 调用 `WorkloadManager.Start(ctx)`  \n24: **THEN** HTTP 服务器在指定地址开始监听  \n25: **AND** 就绪探针端点返回 200\n26: \n27: ### Scenario: 服务器 graceful shutdown\n28: \n29: **GIVEN** 服务器正在运行  \n30: **WHEN** 上下文被取消或收到终止信号  \n31: **THEN** 服务器停止接受新请求  \n32: **AND** 正在处理的请求完成后再退出  \n33: **AND** 返回码为 0\n34: \n35: ### Scenario: 端口冲突\n36: \n37: **GIVEN** 目标端口已被其他进程占用  \n38: **WHEN** 调用 `WorkloadManager.Start(ctx)`  \n39: **THEN** 返回端口占用错误  \n40: **AND** 服务器不启动\n41: \n42: ---\n43: \n44: ## Requirement: AgentRuntime CRUD API\n45: \n46: **ID:** REQ-002  \n47: **Priority:** P0  \n48: \n49: 系统 MUST 提供 AgentRuntime 资源的 CRUD HTTP 端点。\n50: \n51: ### Scenario: 创建 AgentRuntime\n52: \n53: **GIVEN** 有效的 AgentRuntime 创建请求体（JSON）  \n54: **WHEN** 发送 `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes`  \n55: **THEN** 返回 201 Created  \n56: **AND** 响应体包含创建的 AgentRuntime 对象（含 metadata.uid 和 creationTimestamp）\n57: \n58: ### Scenario: 获取 AgentRuntime 列表\n59: \n60: **GIVEN** 命名空间中存在多个 AgentRuntime 资源  \n61: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/agentruntimes?namespace=<ns>`  \n62: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n63: **AND** 响应体为 AgentRuntimeList，包含匹配的 items\n64: \n65: ### Scenario: 获取单个 AgentRuntime\n66: \n67: **GIVEN** 命名空间中存在名为 `my-runtime` 的 AgentRuntime  \n68: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/agentruntimes/my-runtime?namespace=<ns>`  \n69: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n70: **AND** 响应体为该 AgentRuntime 对象\n71: \n72: ### Scenario: 获取不存在的 AgentRuntime\n73: \n74: **GIVEN** 命名空间中不存在指定的 AgentRuntime  \n75: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/agentruntimes/nonexistent?namespace=<ns>`  \n76: **THEN** 返回 404 Not Found\n77: \n78: ### Scenario: 更新 AgentRuntime\n79: \n80: **GIVEN** 已存在的 AgentRuntime 和有效的更新请求体  \n81: **WHEN** 发送 `PUT /api/v1/agentruntimes/<name>?namespace=<ns>`  \n82: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n83: **AND** 响应体包含更新后的对象（resourceVersion 已变更）\n84: \n85: ### Scenario: 删除 AgentRuntime\n86: \n87: **GIVEN** 已存在的 AgentRuntime  \n88: **WHEN** 发送 `DELETE /api/v1/agentruntimes/<name>?namespace=<ns>`  \n89: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n90: **AND** 资源被标记删除\n91: \n92: ---\n93: \n94: ## Requirement: CodeInterpreter CRUD API\n95: \n96: **ID:** REQ-003  \n97: **Priority:** P0  \n98: \n99: 系统 MUST 提供 CodeInterpreter 资源的 CRUD HTTP 端点。\n100: \n101: ### Scenario: 创建 CodeInterpreter\n102: \n103: **GIVEN** 有效的 CodeInterpreter 创建请求体（JSON）  \n104: **WHEN** 发送 `POST /api/v1/codeinterpreters`  \n105: **THEN** 返回 201 Created  \n106: **AND** 响应体包含创建的 CodeInterpreter 对象\n107: \n108: ### Scenario: 获取 CodeInterpreter 列表\n109: \n110: **GIVEN** 命名空间中存在多个 CodeInterpreter 资源  \n111: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/codeinterpreters?namespace=<ns>`  \n112: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n113: **AND** 响应体为 CodeInterpreterList\n114: \n115: ### Scenario: 获取单个 CodeInterpreter\n116: \n117: **GIVEN** 命名空间中存在名为 `my-interpreter` 的 CodeInterpreter  \n118: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/codeinterpreters/my-interpreter?namespace=<ns>`  \n119: **THEN** 返回 200 OK\n120: \n121: ### Scenario: 更新 CodeInterpreter\n122: \n123: **GIVEN** 已存在的 CodeInterpreter 和有效的更新请求体  \n124: **WHEN** 发送 `PUT /api/v1/codeinterpreters/<name>?namespace=<ns>`  \n125: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n126: **AND** 响应体包含更新后的对象\n127: \n128: ### Scenario: 删除 CodeInterpreter\n129: \n130: **GIVEN** 已存在的 CodeInterpreter  \n131: **WHEN** 发送 `DELETE /api/v1/codeinterpreters/<name>?namespace=<ns>`  \n132: **THEN** 返回 200 OK\n133: \n134: ---\n135: \n136: ## Requirement: 请求验证与错误处理\n137: \n138: **ID:** REQ-004  \n139: **Priority:** P0  \n140: \n141: 系统 MUST 验证请求参数并返回结构化错误响应。\n142: \n143: ### Scenario: 缺少必填字段\n144: \n145: **GIVEN** 缺少 `metadata.name` 的创建请求  \n146: **WHEN** 发送 `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes`  \n147: **THEN** 返回 400 Bad Request  \n148: **AND** 响应体包含错误码和错误消息\n149: \n150: ### Scenario: 缺少 namespace 参数\n151: \n152: **GIVEN** 未提供 namespace 查询参数的列表请求  \n153: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /api/v1/agentruntimes`  \n154: **THEN** 返回 400 Bad Request  \n155: **AND** 错误消息指明缺少 namespace 参数\n156: \n157: ### Scenario: 无效的 JSON 请求体\n158: \n159: **GIVEN** 格式错误的 JSON 请求体  \n160: **WHEN** 发送 `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes`  \n161: **THEN** 返回 400 Bad Request  \n162: **AND** 错误消息说明 JSON 解析失败\n163: \n164: ### Scenario: 未注册的路由\n165: \n166: **GIVEN** 任意未注册的路径  \n167: **WHEN** 发送请求到该路径  \n168: **THEN** 返回 404 Not Found\n169: \n170: ---\n171: \n172: ## Requirement: 健康检查端点\n173: \n174: **ID:** REQ-005  \n175: **Priority:** P1  \n176: \n177: 系统 MUST 提供健康检查和就绪检查端点。\n178: \n179: ### Scenario: 存活探针\n180: \n181: **GIVEN** 服务器已启动  \n182: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /healthz`  \n183: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n184: **AND** 响应体包含 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n185: \n186: ### Scenario: 就绪探针\n187: \n188: **GIVEN** 服务器已启动且 informer 缓存已同步  \n189: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /readyz`  \n190: **THEN** 返回 200 OK  \n191: **AND** 响应体包含 `{\"status\": \"ready\"}`\n192: \n193: ### Scenario: 未就绪状态\n194: \n195: **GIVEN** 服务器已启动但 informer 缓存未同步  \n196: **WHEN** 发送 `GET /readyz`  \n197: **THEN** 返回 503 Service Unavailable\n198: \n199: ---\n200: \n201: ## Requirement: Informer 缓存集成\n202: \n203: **ID:** REQ-006  \n204: **Priority:** P1  \n205: \n206: 系统 MUST 使用 SharedInformerFactory 缓存 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 资源。\n207: \n208: ### Scenario: Informer 启动时缓存同步\n209: \n210: **GIVEN** 有效的 Kubernetes 集群连接  \n211: **WHEN** WorkloadManager 初始化  \n212: **THEN** SharedInformerFactory 启动  \n213: **AND** AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter informers 开始同步缓存\n214: \n215: ### Scenario: 列表请求使用缓存\n216: \n217: **GIVEN** Informer 缓存已同步  \n218: **WHEN** 发送列表请求 `GET /api/v1/agentruntimes?namespace=<ns>`  \n219: **THEN** 响应数据来自 informer lister 缓存  \n220: **AND** 不直接调用 Kubernetes API\n221: \n222: ### Scenario: 创建/更新/删除请求直连 API\n223: \n224: **GIVEN** 写操作请求  \n225: **WHEN** 发送 POST/PUT/DELETE 请求  \n226: **THEN** 请求直接转发到 Kubernetes API server  \n227: **AND** 响应返回后 informer 缓存最终一致更新\n\n(End of file - total 227 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# delta-spec: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## Context\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n\nWorkloadManager 提供 HTTP 服务框架，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载的生命周期。基于 `client-go` 生成的 Kubernetes typed client 与 informer 机制，对外暴露 RESTful API。\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: HTTP Server 初始化与生命周期\n\n**ID:** REQ-001  \n**Priority:** P0  \n\n系统 MUST 提供一个可配置的 HTTP 服务器，支持 graceful shutdown。\n\n### Scenario: 服务器正常启动","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775813374397,"end":1775813374404}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813375600,"sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","part":{"id":"prt_d76b9b263001gkKeckT0f14i5F","messageID":"msg_d76b992c8001CQ05FwcsydR5xX","sessionID":"ses_28948eb46ffeUQhCBpppPNpJ6U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_af0b7da08f934b6d9b3f95c0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: Extract shared types (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`) and constants from `codeinterpreter_types.go` into dedicated files, establishing a clear ownership model for the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `pkg/apis`\n8: **Language:** Go\n9: **Size:** S\n10: \n11: ## Problem Statement\n12: \n13: The current codebase has several organizational issues:\n14: \n15: 1. **`TargetPort`** is defined in `codeinterpreter_types.go` but consumed by both `AgentRuntimeSpec.Ports` and `CodeInterpreterSpec.Ports`. This creates an implicit cross-CRD dependency and makes it unclear where new shared types should go.\n16: \n17: 2. **`ProtocolType`** and its constants (`ProtocolTypeHTTP`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS`) live in `codeinterpreter_types.go` despite being semantically generic — any future CRD that exposes network ports would need to reference them.\n18: \n19: 3. **No dedicated file for shared types.** As the API surface grows (e.g., future CRDs like `SessionManager`, `Gateway`), there is no canonical location for types shared across CRDs.\n20: \n21: 4. **Kind constants and `SchemeGroupVersion`** are split between `register.go` and `groupversion_info.go`. While functional, the separation is inconsistent with the kubebuilder convention of a single `groupversion_info.go`.\n22: \n23: ## Goals\n24: \n25: - Provide a canonical home for types and constants shared across CRDs within the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group.\n26: - Maintain 100% backward compatibility — no import path changes, no API-breaking renames.\n27: - Keep CRD-specific types (`AuthModeType`, `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`, `SandboxTemplate`) in their respective type files.\n28: - Ensure `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` continues to regenerate correctly.\n29: \n30: ## Non-Goals\n31: \n32: - Multi-version API support (v1beta1, v2, etc.)\n33: - CRD validation webhook scaffolding\n34: - Conversion webhook setup\n35: \n36: ## Design\n37: \n38: ### File Structure\n39: \n40: ```\n41: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n42: ├── doc.go                        # unchanged\n43: ├── groupversion_info.go          # merge: absorb SchemeGroupVersion + Resource() from register.go\n44: ├── types.go                      # NEW: shared types (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n45: ├── constants.go                  # NEW: shared constants (ProtocolTypeHTTP, ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n46: ├── agent_type.go                 # remove TargetPort/ProtocolType references → import from types.go (same package, no import change)\n47: ├── codeinterpreter_types.go      # remove TargetPort/ProtocolType/AuthModeType → keep only AuthModeType + CRD types\n48: ├── register.go                   # REMOVE: contents merged into groupversion_info.go\n49: ├── zz_generated.deepcopy.go      # regenerated\n50: └── *_test.go                     # updated to match new file layout\n51: ```\n52: \n53: ### New File: `types.go`\n54: \n55: Contains types shared across multiple CRDs within the same API version.\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: package v1alpha1\n59: \n60: // ProtocolType defines the network protocol for port exposure.\n61: type ProtocolType string\n62: \n63: const (\n64: \tProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n65: \tProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n66: )\n67: \n68: // TargetPort describes a network port exposed by a sandbox runtime.\n69: type TargetPort struct {\n70: \tPathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n71: \tName       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n72: \tPort       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n73: \tProtocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n74: }\n75: ```\n76: \n77: **Rationale:** `ProtocolType` and its constants are co-located because the constants have no meaning without the type. `TargetPort` is placed in the same file because it is the primary consumer of `ProtocolType` and is itself shared.\n78: \n79: ### New File: `constants.go`\n80: \n81: Reserved for future shared constants that are not tied to a specific type (e.g., well-known annotation keys, label selectors, default values). Initially empty or minimal:\n82: \n83: ```go\n84: package v1alpha1\n85: \n86: // Well-known annotation keys used across AgentCube CRDs.\n87: const (\n88: \tAnnotationKeyRuntime = \"agentcube.io/runtime\"\n89: \tAnnotationKeyVersion = \"agentcube.io/version\"\n90: )\n91: ```\n92: \n93: **Rationale:** These annotation strings are currently duplicated inline in test files. Centralizing them prevents drift and enables `kubectl get` label selectors to reference a single source of truth.\n94: \n95: ### Modified: `groupversion_info.go`\n96: \n97: Absorbs the contents of `register.go` to follow the kubebuilder convention of a single group-version info file:\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: package v1alpha1\n101: \n102: import (\n103: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n104: \t\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n105: )\n106: \n107: var (\n108: \tGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n109: \n110: \t// SchemeGroupVersion is an alias to GroupVersion for backward compatibility\n111: \t// with client-go generated code that references this name.\n112: \tSchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n113: \n114: \tSchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n115: \n116: \tAddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n117: )\n118: \n119: // Resource returns the GroupVersionResource for the given resource name.\n120: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n121: \treturn GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n122: }\n123: \n124: // Kind constants for both CRDs.\n125: var (\n126: \tCodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n127: \tCodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n128: \tCodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n129: \tCodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n130: \n131: \tAgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n132: \tAgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n133: \tAgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n134: )\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### Modified: `codeinterpreter_types.go`\n138: \n139: Remove `ProtocolType`, its constants, and `TargetPort`. Keep `AuthModeType` (CRD-specific) and the CodeInterpreter CRD types:\n140: \n141: ```go\n142: package v1alpha1\n143: \n144: import (\n145: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n146: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n147: )\n148: \n149: // AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for CodeInterpreter.\n150: type AuthModeType string\n151: \n152: const (\n153: \tAuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n154: \tAuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n155: )\n156: \n157: // +genclient\n158: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n159: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n160: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n161: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n162: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n163: type CodeInterpreter struct { ... }\n164: \n165: // ... (CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, CodeInterpreterList unchanged)\n166: ```\n167: \n168: ### Modified: `agent_type.go`\n169: \n170: No structural changes — `TargetPort` and `ProtocolType` remain accessible because they are in the same package. The file continues to compile without modification.\n171: \n172: ### Deleted: `register.go`\n173: \n174: All contents merged into `groupversion_info.go`. The `Resource()` helper and Kind constants are now co-located with `GroupVersion` and `SchemeBuilder`.\n175: \n176: ## Backward Compatibility\n177: \n178: | Concern | Resolution |\n179: |---------|-----------|\n180: | Import paths | No change — all types remain in `package v1alpha1` |\n181: | Type names | No renames — `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `ProtocolTypeHTTP`, etc. keep their identifiers |\n182: | JSON serialization | Unchanged — struct tags are preserved |\n183: | `SchemeGroupVersion` alias | Preserved for client-go generated code |\n184: | `Resource()` helper | Preserved with identical signature |\n185: | Kind constants | Preserved with identical names and values |\n186: | DeepCopy methods | Regenerated by `make gen-client`; `TargetPort.DeepCopyInto` is a no-op copy (all fields are value types) |\n187: \n188: ## Testing Strategy\n189: \n190: ### Unit Tests\n191: \n192: | Test File | Coverage |\n193: |-----------|----------|\n194: | `types_test.go` | `ProtocolType` constant values, `TargetPort` zero-value defaults, `TargetPort` DeepCopy isolation |\n195: | `constants_test.go` | Well-known annotation key values |\n196: | `groupversion_info_test.go` (updated) | All Kind constants, `SchemeGroupVersion` alias, `Resource()` helper, scheme registration for both CRDs |\n197: | `agent_type_test.go` (unchanged) | Existing tests continue to pass — `TargetPort` and `ProtocolType` are still accessible from the same package |\n198: | `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` (unchanged) | Existing tests continue to pass — `AuthModeType` remains in the same file |\n199: \n200: ### Test Cases for `types_test.go`\n201: \n202: ```\n203: TestProtocolTypeConstants\n204:   - ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"\n205:   - ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"\n206:   - ProtocolTypeHTTP != ProtocolTypeHTTPS\n207: \n208: TestTargetPortDefaults\n209:   - Zero-value TargetPort: Port==0, empty Name/PathPrefix, empty Protocol\n210: \n211: TestTargetPortWithAllFields\n212:   - All fields set, verify JSON tags\n213: \n214: TestTargetPortDeepCopy\n215:   - DeepCopy produces independent copy\n216:   - Modifying copy does not affect original\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### Test Cases for `constants_test.go`\n220: \n221: ```\n222: TestWellKnownAnnotationKeys\n223:   - AnnotationKeyRuntime == \"agentcube.io/runtime\"\n224:   - AnnotationKeyVersion == \"agentcube.io/version\"\n225: ```\n226: \n227: ### Regression Tests\n228: \n229: Run the full existing test suite to verify no breakage:\n230: \n231: ```bash\n232: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v\n233: ```\n234: \n235: All existing tests must pass without modification (same-package visibility ensures `TargetPort` and `ProtocolType` remain accessible).\n236: \n237: ## Code Generation\n238: \n239: After file restructuring, regenerate:\n240: \n241: ```bash\n242: make gen-client\n243: ```\n244: \n245: This runs `hack/update-codegen.sh` which invokes `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with `--with-watch`. Expected output:\n246: \n247: - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` — regenerated with `TargetPort` DeepCopy methods (no functional change, as `TargetPort` contains only value types)\n248: - `client-go/` — no changes (generated code references types by package, not by file)\n249: \n250: ## Migration Steps\n251: \n252: 1. Create `types.go` with `ProtocolType`, its constants, and `TargetPort`\n253: 2. Create `constants.go` with well-known annotation keys\n254: 3. Merge `register.go` contents into `groupversion_info.go`\n255: 4. Delete `register.go`\n256: 5. Remove `ProtocolType`, its constants, and `TargetPort` from `codeinterpreter_types.go`\n257: 6. Create `types_test.go` and `constants_test.go`\n258: 7. Update `register_test.go` → rename to `groupversion_info_test.go` (or merge)\n259: 8. Run `make gen-client` to regenerate DeepCopy\n260: 9. Run `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v` to verify\n261: \n262: ## Risks and Mitigations\n263: \n264: | Risk | Mitigation |\n265: |------|-----------|\n266: | `make gen-client` fails due to file reorganization | The code generator scans the package, not individual files. As long as `doc.go` markers and type definitions are intact, regeneration succeeds. |\n267: | External consumers import specific files | Go imports are at the package level, not file level. No external breakage possible. |\n268: | Merge conflicts during active development | This is a small, self-contained refactoring (S size). Should be merged during a low-activity window. |\n\n(End of file - total 268 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Overview\n\nExtract shared types (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`) and constants from `codeinterpreter_types.go` into dedicated files, establishing a clear ownership model for the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package.\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## Problem Statement\n\nThe current codebase has several organizational issues:\n\n1. **`TargetPort`** is defined in `codeinterpreter_types.go` but consumed by both `AgentRuntimeSpec.Ports` and `CodeInterpreterSpec.Ports`. This creates an implicit cross-CRD dependency and makes it unclear where new shared types should go.\n\n2. **`ProtocolType`** and its constants (`ProtocolTypeHTTP`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS`) live in `codeinterpreter_types.go` despite being semantically generic — any future CRD that exposes network ports would need to reference them.\n\n3. **No dedicated file for shared types.** As the API surface grows (e.g., future CRDs like `SessionManager`, `Gateway`), there is no canonical location for types shared across CRDs.\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775813375587,"end":1775813375596}}}}
